org.opendaylight.yang.gen.v1.urn.ietf.params.xml.ns.yang.ietf.netconf.monitoring.rev101004

Interface CommonCounters

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataContainer, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Session, Statistics

    public interface CommonCounters
extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject
    Counters that exist both per session, and also globally, accumulated from all sessions.

    This class represents the following YANG schema fragment defined in module ietf-netconf-monitoring
    (Source path: META-INF/yang/ietf-netconf-monitoring.yang): 

     grouping common-counters {
     leaf in-rpcs {
         type zero-based-counter32;
     }
     leaf in-bad-rpcs {
         type zero-based-counter32;
     }
     leaf out-rpc-errors {
         type zero-based-counter32;
     }
     leaf out-notifications {
         type zero-based-counter32;
     }
 }
    The schema path to identify an instance is ietf-netconf-monitoring/common-counters
